The Reason
~~~~~~~~~~
This game was made to prove you don't need flashy graphics to have a 
good larf. Me and my brother were hooked on it for ages because it's 
just different, and it does get you on edge, especially with the speed
of some of the viruses, together with the eerie electronic sound FX.
There's no bobs, no sprites, no fancy parallax scrolling, no animation
no mind-bending puzzles... just a nice little game. That'll have you 
PULLING YOUR GODDAMNED HAIR OUT!!!!!! Ahem.


